    "Threat actors could breach data security and privacy by exploiting drone system flaws.",
    "Additionally, drones' extensive data transmission and collection pose questions regarding data security and possible exploitation.",
    "The evolution of the Internet of Drone Things (IoDT) can only be maximized with the help of a security architecture to be implemented.",
    "• This paper focuses on the new trends in drone safety, security, and privacy aspects, as well as the field of the Internet of Drones (IoD).",
    "It underlines the need to develop protective measures to create reliable and robust drone networks that would not be vulnerable to hackers and corresponding breaches."
